column5: I had illusions of the Leafs winning the Stanley cup. Seriously though, my back yard thermometer read 102F late this afternoon.  So how hot was it where you live??
It was so hot today our sermon was very short: " If you think it is hot now, just wait"
it was so hot viagra couldn't stop it from melting
It was so hot today the Campbell Soup Co. has changed the directions on its cans to, "Just pour and eat."

it's so hot , I had to take a pee while I was on a boat but it evaporated before it hit the lake  it's so hot all the fish I caught came out half baked  It's so hot that I saw two trees fighting over a dog.  It's so hot, today I saw a chicken lay a fried egg.

It was so hot today I saw a funeral procession pull into a Dairy Queen.  t's So Hot....... I saw a squirrel picking up nuts with pot holders!!  It's So Hot....... cows give powdered milk!!  It's so hot, I can roast marshmallows on s stick, without a fire  it's do hot all my popcorn kernels popped in the cupboards
It's so hot... the perch were on fire!
So hot today we didn't walk bar to bar.. we used the streetcar!
It was so hot today that I saw a lawyer with his hands outside of his clients pockets.
it was so hot even bad sex was hot sex
it was so hot....the wax in my ears started on fire  yeah but it's a great day to pick up girls, a few told me I was hot.....oh yeah I.m hot
its so hot, the squirrels are handling their nuts with potholders....
Why watch letterman when you got Terrys top ten list for everything
it's so hot I had to fight off the Armish for the last air conditioner at CTC  it's so hot the Jehovah Witness gave up knocking on doors and hired a telemarketing company
It was so hot today I went to work early cause there A/C is better then mine
HA! Love'em.
It was so hot that I saw a dog chasing a cat and they wre walking
It was sooooo hot Chuck Norris turned the sun down...

it's so hot the Jehovah Witness gave up knocking on doors and hired a telemarketing company....in India....................................................India...  Hello my friend and can I be interesting you in the watchtower.....nevermind     it's so hot the Jehovah Witness are putting windows in their place of worship......   I am going to hell aren't I....LOL
[ I am going to hell aren't I....LOL     Now that's a hot place!
Give it a week. It'll be cooler there
it's so hot today I saw the proverbial hand basket on it's way to hell...to cool off    ok, the brain is dead I hope no more it's to hot jokes jump into my head
It's so hot today that Terry finally shut up....
It was so hot the Pilsbury French Loaf I bought at the grocery store was ready to serve by the time I got home!!!!
